column3: CH3Cl labile organic carbon

Relative abundance of 13C isotope (i.e. 13C/(13C+12C)) in chloroform labile organic carbon extracted by 0.05 Potassium sulfate (1:4 w/w soil:extractant). The value is calculated using two-pool mixing model to separate isotope signal of chloroform flush from background. The raw data (i.e. 13C atm in potassium sulfate extract after chloroform fumigation of soil) are available upon request.
